# WebM VP8 Codec SDK

media-libs/libvpx -altivec -debug -doc postproc -static-libs threads

# altivec	Add support for optimizations for G4 and G5/ppc970 processors
# debug		Enable extra debug codepaths, like asserts and extra output. 
# doc		Add extra documentation (API, Javadoc, etc). 
# postproc	Enable additional post processing filters
# static-libs	Build static versions of dynamic libraries as well
# test	Workaround to pull in packages needed to run with FEATURES=test. Portage-2.1.2 handles this internally, so don't set it in make.conf/package.use anymore
# threads	Add threads support for various packages. Usually pthreads
